 data-framer-name=\"Container\" style=\"--12gp6ac: 8px 12px 8px 12px; background-color: rgb(128, 72, 245); border-radius: 100px; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-17gd20u\" style=\"--extracted-r6o4lv: rgb(255, 255, 255); --framer-link-text-color: rgb(0, 153, 255); --framer-link-text-decoration: underline; transform: none; opacity: 1;\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-pk5f8l\" data-styles-preset=\"Epu0NqScc\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, rgb(255, 255, 255))\">WooCommerce App</p></div></div></a><!--/$--></div></div></div></header></div></div></div></div><style data-framer-html-style=\"\">html body { background: var(--token-37e8afd6-496b-4761-a610-4c3bcbf28d89, rgb(255, 255, 255)); }</style><div data-framer-root=\"\" class=\"framer-OE08f framer-dNysf framer-98yyr framer-Tjj7s framer-12t9mrb\" style=\"min-height:100vh;width:auto;display:contents\"><section class=\"framer-1knotgc\" data-framer-name=\"Page Title\"><div class=\"framer-ry3k63\" data-framer-name=\"Inner\"><div class=\"framer-dr1onj\"><div class=\"framer-1gl0v5v\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><h1 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-hqv2qo\" data-styles-preset=\"kx7Q6WsHD\">We Built Verve Because We Needed It Ourselves</h1></div><div class=\"framer-10p0t9t\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\">Before we wrote a line of code, we were running e-commerce stores, struggling to plan inventory and constantly reacting to stockouts and overstocks. Verve is the tool we wish we had — now we’re sharing it with you.</p></div></div><div class=\"framer-br3mj7\" data-framer-name=\"About Us\"><div class=\"framer-16uaj56\" data-framer-name=\"Mission and Vision\"><div class=\"framer-z0ca6d\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><h5 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-16wf23l\" data-styles-preset=\"whYfzqmcB\">Say goodbye to spreadsheets and headaches….</h5></div><div class=\"framer-b3qfsm\"><div class=\"framer-1ktvvne\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">We’re not just building forecasting software — we’re building the tool we <em class=\"framer-text\">wished</em> we had when we were running our own e-commerce businesses.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">Before starting Verve, we were deep in the day-to-day of buying, planning, and managing inventory. We’ve dealt with the stress of guessing how much to order, the frustration of stockouts during peak sales, and the regret of sitting on piles of dead stock we couldn’t move. Sound familiar?</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">Most of the tools we tried were either too complex, too generic, or still left us knee-deep in spreadsheets. So we decided to create something better — something made specifically for e-commerce teams who want clear, confident answers about what to order and when.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">Verve is built by e-commerce buyers, for e-commerce buyers. It uses AI to handle the heavy lifting — so you can stop second-guessing your decisions and start focusing on growth.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">We know how hard this can be. That’s exactly why we’re here to help.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1lb16r3\" data-styles-preset=\"Pu00R26H5\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--token-c2a3bf50-9c5c-48a1-a955-71074a7a38d9, rgba(18, 19, 22, 0.6))\">— The Verve Team</p></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><div id=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"framer-1h2kvss\"></div><div class=\"framer-lsv2fh\" data-framer-name=\"Footer\"><div class=\"ssr-variant hidden-v3h10d hidden-907ff8\"><div class=\"framer-ihe3tg-container\"><footer class=\"framer-qm2kR framer-98yyr framer-oXIyl framer-zKijR framer-LWPyD framer-qm5p50 framer-v-qm5p50\" data-framer-name=\"Desktop\" style=\"background-color: rgb(19, 33, 68); width: 100%; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-15ufsj5\" data-framer-name=\"Inner\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-6ttnxu\" data-framer-name=\"List\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-1ofpdd9\" data-framer-name=\"Title\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-8wi8wv-container\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-uL3sp framer-1i9bryg framer-v-1i9bryg framer-1hend0p\" data-framer-name=\"Default\" style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%; opacity: 1;\" href=\"./\"><div class=\"framer-4f2q0f\" data-framer-name=\"Logo\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0\" data-framer-background-image-wrapper=\"true\"><img decoding=\"auto\" width=\"940\" height=\"469\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 150px, (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) 367px, (max-width: 809.98px) 150px\" srcset=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/zplhvSQDvA45ptNBhwmtoWBGiU0.png?scale-down-to=512 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/zplhvSQDvA45ptNBhwmtoWBGiU0.png 940w\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/zplhvSQDvA45ptNBhwmtoWBGiU0.pn