  "bodyText": "Home\n\nAbout\n\nContact\n\nShopify App\n\nWooCommerce App\n\nWe Built Verve Because We Needed It Ourselves\n\nBefore we wrote a line of code, we were running e-commerce stores, struggling to plan inventory and constantly reacting to stockouts and overstocks. Verve is the tool we wish we had — now we’re sharing it with you.\n\nSay goodbye to spreadsheets and headaches….\n\nWe’re not just building forecasting software — we’re building the tool we wished we had when we were running our own e-commerce businesses.\n\nBefore starting Verve, we were deep in the day-to-day of buying, planning, and managing inventory. We’ve dealt with the stress of guessing how much to order, the frustration of stockouts during peak sales, and the regret of sitting on piles of dead stock we couldn’t move. Sound familiar?\n\nMost of the tools we tried were either too complex, too generic, or still left us knee-deep in spreadsheets. So we decided to create something better — something made specifically for e-commerce teams who want clear, confident answers about what to order and when.\n\nVerve is built by e-commerce buyers, for e-commerce buyers. It uses AI to handle the heavy lifting — so you can stop second-guessing your decisions and start focusing on growth.\n\nWe know how hard this can be. That’s exactly why we’re here to help.\n\n— The Verve Team\n\nAI Forecasting Software for E-Commerce Businesses\n\nQuick Links\n\nHome\n\nAbout\n\nPricing\n\nWhy Verve AI\n\nContact\n\nBlog\n\nTools\n\nImportant\n\nVerve AI Shopify\n\nVerve AI WooCommerce\n\nTwitter\n\nPrivacy Policy\n\nTerms\n\nFAQ\n\nGet in Touch\n\nHello@GetVerveAI.com\n\nCopyright © 2026 Verve AI. All rights reserved.",
